item.title: CVE-2022-22547|2024-08-03T03:14:55.753Z -- sap%20se -- simple%20diagnostics%20agent
item.description: Simple Diagnostics Agent - versions 1.0 (up to version 1.57.), allows an attacker to access information which would otherwise be restricted via a random port 9000-65535. This allows information gathering which could be used exploit future open-source security exploits.
